[10:56] <lizmat> or use a Callable as the replacement:

[10:56] <lizmat> m: my $c; say "foobarbaz".subst("o", { ++$c; "e" }, :g); say $c

[10:56] <camelia> rakudo-moar 81ea8224b: OUTPUT: «feebarbaz␤2␤»

